  <id>dev.pwgenrust.PwGen</id>
  <name>PwGen</name>
  <summary>Advanced Password &amp; Secrets Manager built in Rust</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      PwGen is a modern, secure password and secrets manager built in Rust with enterprise-grade security,
      modern UI, and cross-platform support.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AES-256-GCM encryption with Argon2 key derivation</li>
      <li>Cross-platform GUI and CLI interfaces</li>
      <li>Browser import (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge, Opera, Brave)</li>
      <li>SSH key and API token management</li>
      <li>Secure document storage with optional compression</li>
      <li>Zero-knowledge architecture - your data never leaves your device</li>
      <li>30-40% smaller binaries with v1.2 optimization</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
